      • getLeftDelimitedIdentifier

        public String getLeftDelimitedIdentifier()
        Description copied from class: JdbcExtractor
        Default DelimitedIdentifier is 'double quotes', but that would make the column name case sensitive in some of the systems, e.g. Oracle. Queries may fail if (1) enableDelimitedIdentifier is true, and (2) Queried system is case sensitive when using double quotes as delimited identifier, and (3) Intended column name does not match the column name in the schema including case.
        Overrides:
